                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for preparing methanol from coal",
                    "一种煤制甲醇装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a coal-to-methanol device and method.The coal-to-methanol device comprises a coal gasification unit, a washing and cooling unit, a water gas conversion unit, a low-temperature methanol washing unit and a first methanol synthesis unit, a coal inlet of the coal gasification unit is connected with a coal source, and an oxygen inlet of the coal gasification unit is connected with an oxygen source; a carbon dioxide gas outlet of the low-temperature methanol washing unit is connected with a reforming system, a carbon dioxide gas inlet of a carbon dioxide dry reforming unit in the reforming system is connected with a carbon dioxide gas outlet of the low-temperature methanol washing unit, an outlet is connected with a washing and purifying unit, and an outlet of the washing and purifying unit is connected with a second methanol synthesis unit; methane and carbon dioxide are introduced for dry reforming, natural gas energy and captured carbon dioxide are used for performing reforming reaction, green hydrogen prepared by combining renewable energy is used for reconstructing synthesis gas and generating methanol, so that carbon dioxide generated in the traditional coal-to-methanol process is recycled, the emission amount of carbon dioxide is greatly reduced, and the production cost is reduced. The methanol yield is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种煤制甲醇装置及方法，采用煤气化单元、洗涤冷却单元、水煤气变换单元、低温甲醇洗单元和第一甲醇合成单元，煤气化单元的煤炭进口连接煤炭源，煤气化单元的氧气进口连接氧源，低温甲醇洗单元的二氧化碳气体出口连接有重整系统，重整系统中的二氧化碳干重整单元的二氧化碳气体入口连接低温甲醇洗单元的二氧化碳气体出口，出口连接洗涤净化单元，洗涤净化单元的出口连接有第二甲醇合成单元，通过引入甲烷二氧化碳干重整，利用天然气能源与捕获到的二氧化碳进行重整反应，再结合可再生能源制得的绿色氢气重构合成气，生成甲醇，使传统煤制甲醇过程中产生的二氧化碳得到资源化利用，极大地降低了二氧化碳的排放量，提高了甲醇产量。"
                }
            ]
